      "results": {
        "code": "SUCCESS",
        "msg": [
          {
            "type": "TEXT",
            "data": "[2025-11-24 15:20:01] Step 0\u003e Loading data (Bulk)\n[2025-11-24 15:20:01] Loading data from HDFS CSV: /Data/soh/result/integrate/all/soh_base_result_all.csv\n[2025-11-24 15:20:05] Step 0 - Initial data count: 2342708\n[2025-11-24 15:20:05] Converting \u0027soh\u0027 string column back to ArrayType...\n[2025-11-24 15:20:05] Step 1\u003e Filtering data (Charge only, etc.)\n[2025-11-24 15:20:07] After Step 1 filtering: 1,863,317 rows\n[2025-11-24 15:20:07] Step 2\u003e Numbering charge sequence\n[2025-11-24 15:20:07] Step 3\u003e Summarizing by sequence\n[2025-11-24 15:20:07] Step 4\u003e Calculating accumulated DoD (per vehicle)\n[2025-11-24 15:20:07] Collecting summary data to Pandas for Linear Regression (per vehicle)...\n[2025-11-24 15:20:17] Calculating initial_dod for 8 vehicles...\n[2025-11-24 15:20:17] Step 5\u003e Calculating C-rate\n[2025-11-24 15:20:17] Step 6\u003e Selecting final columns\n[2025-11-24 15:20:27] Final result count: 982 rows\n[2025-11-24 15:20:27] Step 7\u003e Saving results to HDFS\n[2025-11-24 15:20:27] Saving data to HDFS *single file*: /Data/soh/result/integrate/all/soh_summary_result_all.csv\n[2025-11-24 15:20:27] Using temporary save directory: /Data/soh/result/integrate/all/.temp_summary_save_dir_all\n[2025-11-24 15:20:41] Found temporary data file: hdfs://mycluster/Data/soh/result/integrate/all/.temp_summary_save_dir_all/part-00000-b0343991-7998-4959-a295-361da15603bd-c000.csv\n[2025-11-24 15:20:41] Checking for existing file and deleting if present: /Data/soh/result/integrate/all/soh_summary_result_all.csv\n[2025-11-24 15:20:41] Successfully saved to single HDFS file: /Data/soh/result/integrate/all/soh_summary_result_all.csv\nResults saved to HDFS: /Data/soh/result/integrate/all/soh_summary_result_all.csv\n[2025-11-24 15:20:41] Main function finished.\n"
